/x.com/ProfKayaFinance/status/2051608886856094028", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/ProfKayaFinance/status/2051608886856094028", "text": "2.part \nBu gece takip etti\u011fim tum \u015firketler nerdeyse altyap\u0131 oyuncusu sadece $TEM ve $TMDX sa\u011fl\u0131k sekt\u00f6r\u00fcnde. Tempus kabaca yapay zekay\u0131 sa\u011fl\u0131k sekt\u00f6r\u00fc veriyle yeniden in\u015fa etmeye \u00e7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor. Kanser te\u015fhisinden ila\u00e7 geli\u015ftirmeye, gen diziliminden klinik veri lisanslamaya kadar cok geni\u015f bir alandalar. Piyasan\u0131n beklentisi 345M dolar gelir ki bu ge\u00e7en y\u0131la g\u00f6re %35 b\u00fcy\u00fcme demek $TEM k\u00e2r etmiyor hen\u00fcz hatta 2029 \u00f6ncede zor ama gidi\u015f y\u00f6n\u00fc do\u011fru. Ge\u00e7en y\u0131l tam y\u0131l geliri %83 buyudu ve 2026 y\u0131l\u0131 i\u00e7in pozitif d\u00fczeltilmi\u015f FAV\u00d6K hedefi vardi y\u00f6netimin. \u0130la\u00e7 \u015firketleriyle 70'ten fazla veri anla\u015fmas\u0131 ve %26 net gelir tutma oran\u0131 \u015firketin  ne kadar dogru i\u015fler yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 bize g\u00f6steriyor. Merck, Gilead, NYU Langone ile yeni ortakl\u0131klar  kurdular bununla ilgili  earnings call'da bol bol detay duymak istiyorum. Buyume h\u0131z\u0131nda bir yava\u015flama olmasin birde y\u00f6netim \u00f6nceki plana sadik kals\u0131n anla\u015fmalar\u0131n detaylar\u0131da guzelse piyasa zaten \u00fczerine d\u00fc\u015feni yapar diye d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcn\u00fcyorum. E\u011fer sert bi d\u00fc\u015f\u00fc\u015f olursa aliciyim bilan\u00e7oya gore.\n \nVe gelelim portf\u00f6y y\u0131ld\u0131z\u0131na $ALAB. Credo ile beraber kisa bir s\u00fcrede portf\u00f6y\u00fc toparlad\u0131lar. Astera'n\u0131n hikayesi asl\u0131nda s\u0131radan g\u00f6r\u00fcnen ana cok \u00f6nemli bir hik\u00e2ye bunu son bir kac ayda defalarca dile getirdim ondan bu taraf\u0131 ge\u00e7iyorum. Gecen \u00e7eyrekte yillik bazda %92 b\u00fcy\u00fcye \u015firketi marjlarin d\u00fc\u015fmesi y\u00fcz\u00fcnden g\u00fczelce d\u00f6vd\u00fcler. Br\u00fct kar marj\u0131 %75 operasyonel marj\u0131 %41 bunlar neredeyse  yaz\u0131l\u0131m \u015firketi marjlar\u0131 eger y\u00f6netim bize bunu s\u00fcrd\u00fcr\u00fclebilir oldu\u011funu s\u00f6ylerse bilin ki hisse d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcr kalkar ama yeni zirveleri g\u00f6sterir bize tersine bir yakla\u015f\u0131m olursa \u00f6nceki bilan\u00e7odan farks\u0131z olmaz piyasan\u0131n tepkisi. Ge\u00e7en hafta ufak bir k\u00e2r alm\u0131\u015ft\u0131m, onun d\u0131\u015f\u0131nda hem Tempus hem de Astera Labs pozisyonlar\u0131m\u0131 koruyorum.", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 1, "likeCount": 33, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 4499, "createdAt": "Tue May 05 10:24:10 +0000 2026", "lang": "tr", "bookmarkCount": 6, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2051608886856094028", "displayTextRange": [0, 280], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "ProfKayaFinance", "url": "https://x.com/ProfKayaFinance", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/ProfKayaFinance", "id": "1889251650659106817", "name": "Kaya Finance", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2005333727627341824/jxZFSAO3_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1889251650659106817/1747683723", "description": "", "location": "Marseille, France", "followers": 35146, "following": 137, "status": "", "canDm": false, "canMediaTag": true, "createdAt": "Tue Feb 11 09:54:52 +0000 2025", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 25971, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 2381, "statusesCount": 14618, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": ["2051392940820357626"], "profile_bio": {"description": "\u2728\ufe0f AI,Bulut ve Siber G\u00fcvenl